description: The three men and one woman will serve in the Manx parliament's upper chamber for five years.
title: Four elected to Isle of Man's Legislative Council at special House of Keys sitting
title_page: Four elected to Isle of Man's Legislative Council at special House of Keys sitting - BBC News
maintext: Mr Greenhill, a former head of the government's e-gaming and e-business development department, said he was prepared for "five years of really hard work" in the parliament.
